Class EventGcmRegistrationIdUpdated

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.palomamobile.android.sdk.notification.EventGcmRegistrationIdUpdated
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IEvent<String>, IJobEvent<JobUserUpdateGcmRegistrationId,String>

    public class EventGcmRegistrationIdUpdated
extends Object
implements IJobEvent<JobUserUpdateGcmRegistrationId,String>
    Event published on the de.greenrobot.event.EventBus (as returned by ServiceSupport.getEventBus()) whenever a GCM registration id for the client application has been updated on the server. The event contains either the current gcmRegistrationId on request success or throwable on request failure.
